                <h1>Understanding SSBI Clearance Disqualifiers</h1>
                <p>SSBI clearance is crucial for sensitive positions, but certain disqualifiers can hinder the process. These include criminal behavior, poor credit history, illegal drug use, undisclosed foreign contacts, or mental health issues. Understanding these factors can help applicants prepare and improve their chances of obtaining clearance.</p>
